# ModelRouter

Self-hosted LLM gateway powered by LiteLLM. OpenAI-compatible API at `http://127.0.0.1:3000/v1`.

## Key paths

- `config/modelrouter.yaml` — full config (Redis, fallbacks, all providers)
- `config/modelrouter.minimal.yaml` — dev config without Redis
- `scripts/start.sh` / `scripts/load_secrets.py` — startup + 1Password
- `modelrouter/logging_callback.py` — structured JSON request logs
- `agents/` — curated agency-agents prompts for development (SRE, DevOps, MCP builder)
- `deploy/com.modelrouter.plist` — launchd for always-on Mac

## Conventions

- Provider keys via env or 1Password `op://` refs — never commit secrets
- Logical model aliases: `smart`, `fast`, `local`
- Extend via LiteLLM callbacks in `modelrouter/` package
- Always-on target: `kc-mini` (`/Users/kevinreed/dev/modelrouter`)

## Commands

```bash
make install && make daemon && make health
./scripts/deploy-to-mini.sh
```
